Package: python-pyramid-request-log
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Description: A Pyramid Plugin For loggin request
 A pyramid plugin that will log all Request and Response.
 If a json body is available it will also be logged,
 a list of forbidden key can be used to not logged sensitive information.
